# 🎯 Most Asked Interview Question

### Q: What is the difference between a Notebook and a Job?

| Notebook             | Job                                  |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| Contains code        | Executes code                        |
| Manual by default    | Automated                            |
| Used for development | Used for production                  |
| Can be run directly  | Can run notebooks, SQL, Python, etc. |

